x4freetext: energy spread in beam 400 eV and proton current on
Enriched 26Mg, 30Si and 34S produced by hammering of
26Mg, 30Si and 34S ions in Ta backing in
The target thicknesses are ~7 keV (26Mg, 30Si) at
36S consisting of Ag2S (81.1% 36S) deposited on Ta
60 cm3 and a resolution of 3.0 keV at 1.33 MeV,
0, 30, 45, 60 and 90 deg with respect to proton beam
direction shielded with Pb and Cu.
measurements and as monitor of gamma radiation
On. REFERENCE: Eng. and Rus. ref. swapped.
